{"tid":2262529,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強力驅逐避難中國漁船 國台辦：台灣太野蠻令人憤慨！","createTime":"2020-10-29T07:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T15:32:29.000Z","uid":337052,"like":13,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"4c3c7e076dd8fd408cd6b784d5b4d325becc9519","tid":2262529,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:45:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">國台辦回應&ldquo;大陸漁船澎湖避風遭台艦水砲驅離&rdquo;：野蠻</span></strong><br />\n來源：海外網<br />\n<br />\n2020-10-28 10:36<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs1.huanqiucdn.cn/dp/api/images/imageDir/ea1901123908139d09e226504b8718fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs1.huanqiucdn.cn%2Fdp%2Fapi%2Fimages%2FimageDir%2Fea1901123908139d09e226504b8718fa.jpg&h=3bfa63df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖為朱鳳蓮<br />\n<br />\n海外網10月28日電 10月28日上午，國務院台灣事務辦公室舉行例行新聞發布會。國台辦發言人朱鳳蓮就兩岸政黨交流、兩岸軍事互信和兩岸文化往來等熱點問題回答記者提問。<br />\n<br />\n有記者問，據報導，10月23日有20多艘大陸漁船因遭遇7至10級大風，希望進入澎湖附近島嶼避風，卻被台海巡單位強行驅離，請問您對此有何評論？<br />\n<br />\n朱鳳蓮表示，多年以來，大陸方面在沿海多處設立了台灣漁民接待站、接待點，為台灣漁船、漁民避風、補給、搶險等提供救助。相比之下，<span class=\"red\">台灣有關方面野蠻驅離避風大陸漁船的不人道做法，十分令人憤慨。</span>"},{"pid":"2c689d3ffb8c8e981497852147ec12f4459e3ec5","tid":2262529,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:46:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/j6uEOPyAHs0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fj6uEOPyAHs0&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KiqT%2B3fxaX50J59AF9IhbNpo%3D&h=de202a68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/j6uEOPyAHs0</a><br />\n澎湖海象惡劣海巡搏命查緝中國漁船 網友籲直接沒入(艦隊分署提供)"},{"pid":"25f7591e80452a2a6943d384e4dd16c4ea8402d6","tid":2262529,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:46:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BFWTou_MgjE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBFWTou_MgjE&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KiqT%2B3fxaX50J59AF9IhbNpo%3D&h=7bd9aa60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BFWTou_MgjE</a><br />\n臺方水炮驅離大陸避風漁船 國台辦：不人道做法令人憤慨"},{"pid":"2305c88da54766eeb27da870ca46c344be9f3435","tid":2262529,"uid":337052,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:48:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">中國國台辦轟我海巡署野蠻 陸委會：仍會嚴正執法</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n2020/10/28 20:33<br />\n〔記者陳鈺馥／台北報導〕<span class=\"red\">針對中國漁船以避風為名，大舉入侵澎湖南方四島國家公園海域，我海巡署日前派出高雄艦以水砲驅離。中國國台辦今日砲轟我海巡署「野蠻」、「不人道」，令人憤慨；陸委會今晚回擊，這是枉顧事實也污衊我執法人員的說法。</span><br />\n<br />\n陸委會表示，據了解，每年秋冬季都有大批中國漁船假藉避風名義，聚集在澎湖西吉嶼海域，實質上卻是趁機非法拖網捕魚，已嚴重破壞我漁業資源與海洋環境。海巡署月23日發現10餘艘中國籍漁船假藉避風群聚西吉嶼，即予以驅離，遏阻陸船越界作業，展現政府堅定護漁之立場與決心。<br />\n<br />\n陸委會強調，<span class=\"red\">對於越界陸船，我執法機關仍會嚴正執法</span>，本會再度呼籲陸方約束相關人員與船舶，勿放任陸船越界捕撈，以維護海洋漁業資源。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3335213\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3335213&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KiqT%2B3fxaX50J59AF9IhbNpo%3D&h=704f65b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3335213&h=c591b56f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3335213</a>"},{"pid":"92e16579c430d3a33e86068d34cba9e8806bec73","tid":2262529,"uid":11291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:49:59.000Z","msg":"支那：好嬲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a471caf1e261ed689d20785687decbd91a94cde6","tid":2262529,"uid":92125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:50:29.000Z","msg":"太野蠻啦 應該沒收啦"},{"pid":"d4ceb98e2eba590ac6500442960fff4d74403b58","tid":2262529,"uid":66957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:50:46.000Z","msg":"石頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b206b75f962ba524f898a838bac64cd436eae19","tid":2262529,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:51:27.000Z","msg":"Cls"},{"pid":"67f0665965dd2f67f8875725b97e8791f3a7fc1a","tid":2262529,"uid":290404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:52:53.000Z","msg":"避乜鬼，咁有本事返去福建避囉"},{"pid":"93cac9097d83daf9d13e88e7a596dc48ad37c704","tid":2262529,"uid":100638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:53:51.000Z","msg":"隻閪手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543a779ac01b47b7d4ff7e7bdfa780245672a01c","tid":2262529,"uid":143621,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:53:55.000Z","msg":"避咩風吖屌 偷偷地想捉人地海域啲魚啦肯定<br />\n<br />\n撚信你大陸狗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae551424f12b711a15658096752848e67979c9b","tid":2262529,"uid":121146,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:54:16.000Z","msg":"一開始就唔應該入台灣境  你唔入去又何需要避?"},{"pid":"899e8512d69b6b181b73db613d7a54a2d9d41bec","tid":2262529,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:56:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">陸船越界澎湖海域避風 高雄艦水炮驅離20餘艘</span></strong><br />\n2020-10-23 20:26 中央社 / 澎湖縣23日電<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7327/4959037\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7327%2F4959037&h=a8f4f79a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澎湖海域23日東北季風增強，陣風高達10級，海巡署近岸雷達發現大批中國漁船靠近望安西吉島海域避風，艦隊分署指派3000噸高雄艦前往，以發射水砲驅離陸船至澎湖限制水域外，並持續在附近海域監控巡邏。圖／澎湖海巡隊提供<br />\n<br />\n東北季風強勁吹襲，<span class=\"red\">中國大陸漁船20餘艘今天出現在澎湖西吉海域避風，艦隊分署出動3000噸高雄艦前往，以發射水砲方式驅離陸船至澎湖限制水域外。</span><br />\n<br />\n澎湖海域今天東北季風增強，陣風高達10級，海巡署近岸雷達發現大批陸船靠近望安西吉島海域避風。<br />\n<br />\n澎湖海巡屏東艦與巡護九號等，因海象惡劣海面風浪過大無法出海執行，只能作近岸航行，艦隊分署指派3000噸高雄艦前往，以發射水砲驅離陸船至澎湖限制水域外，並持續在附近海域監控巡邏。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7327/4959037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7327%2F4959037&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KiqT%2B3fxaX50J59AF9IhbNpo%3D&h=30208c93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7327/4959037</a>"},{"pid":"d4b60c59e9e0275b32e53a54c452ea43249def58","tid":2262529,"uid":240971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:59:34.000Z","msg":"應該直接射火炮係隻漁船隔離炸起d水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n水炮車枝水喉有d弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3091c0cdf77c7e768697148bc73a1639f697d14","tid":2262529,"uid":263534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:00:46.000Z","msg":"好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d0c2c24ac9911a6f8239cfc80669c9f7bbd24c","tid":2262529,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4b60c59e9e0275b32e53a54c452ea43249def58","tid":2262529,"uid":240971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:59:34.000Z","msg":"應該直接射火炮係隻漁船隔離炸起d水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n水炮車枝水喉有d弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:04:21.000Z","msg":"水砲功率要加強"},{"pid":"8a987af36dd43c1aac47b56397dd5f8752f307ec","tid":2262529,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:12:07.000Z","msg":"落水底避啦支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" clas